name: Kedro
introductoryText:
![kedro](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
  

The blocks interfaces with Kedro workflows. Specify the path to your Kedro workflow and all the names of the input and output files. 

E.g. if you specified in your Kedro workflow that there are 2 input files called input0.csv and data1.csv in the data/01_raw folder within the Kedro project, then use input0 as the file name for the first input and data1 for the second. The first block input will then be routed into input0.csv and the second into data1.csv. Do the same for the output file.
